  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个安全系统的状态图。系统启动后应该直接进入Safe状态，这是正常运行的状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Safe",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，起点到Safe。那如果现场触发急停按钮呢？应该有个EmergencyStop状态吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EmergencyStop",
        "E-Stop Triggered"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Safe可以转到EmergencyStop，触发条件是E-Stop Triggered。急停之后需要人工复位才能回到Safe状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Safe",
        "EmergencyStop",
        "Reset",
        "E-Stop Triggered"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，我加上双向箭头。另外我觉得还需要一个中间状态——比如安全检查没通过的时候，不是直接急停，而是先Warning警告？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Warning",
        "Safety Check Failed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Warning状态很重要。问题修复后可以回到Safe，但如果恶化成Critical Failure，就必须进入EmergencyStop。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Warning",
        "Safe",
        "EmergencyStop",
        "Issue Resolved",
        "Critical Failure"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经画好了Warning的分支。最后EmergencyStop之后呢？系统怎么结束？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EmergencyStop",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "急停最终会导致System Shutdown，也就是终止状态。这是安全设计的最后一步。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EmergencyStop",
        "[*]",
        "System Shutdown"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完成。我检查一下：起点→Safe，Safe可以急停或进入警告，警告可恢复或恶化，急停可复位或关机。结构清晰，符合安全规范。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Safe",
        "EmergencyStop",
        "Warning",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
